{"tid":1708992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想用呢個post整合返因為呢場運動而逝世既名單","createTime":"2019-11-11T19:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T21:57:03.000Z","uid":99402,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf517505f4afaa7fbfb34065a6aabb67d725ece","tid":1708992,"uid":99402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"我希望大家可以合力提供資料<br />\n並將呢份名單用作:<br />\n<br />\n1. 紀念每一位手足 以示我地所有人唔會忘記佢地<br />\n2. 將名字永留於香港歷史入面內 如wiki, 香港網絡大典等<br />\n3. 作為文宣 (我明白係唔太道德 但都唔希望佢地既死就成為一個句號)<br />\n4. 提醒現時仲係戰場既人 唔好被麻目<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以用以下既格式去提交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=========================<br />\n逝世時間:<br />\n2019年XX月XX日XX時XX分 (香港時間)<br />\n<br />\n名字:<br />\nXXX<br />\n<br />\n死因:<br />\nXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX<br />\n<br />\n家屬留言:<br />\nXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX<br />\n<br />\n生前相片:<br />\n-圖-<br />\n<br />\n補充資料:<br />\nXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX<br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個表可能有錯漏<br />\n但都想大家填住先<br />\n<br />\n如果真係太多既話 (雖然唔希望)<br />\n我會開份google form比大家繼續填<br />\n<br />\n最後我會整返個excel出黎比大家用<br />\n<br />\n我可以做既野暫時得咁多<br />\n希望大家可以幫忙完成呢份表<br />\n<br />\nThanks all"},{"pid":"7d3be19a99f15553de1a62ba7a01d0a73cce6457","tid":1708992,"uid":99402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7be616d13f0e26749afb99c513ebaa1efd6816f","tid":1708992,"uid":119181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"320e526167e0a7efd607eb7e89a07567b9570ea4","tid":1708992,"uid":336072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:11:32.000Z","msg":"其實好想知個200位義士既家屬去曬邊"},{"pid":"079aa97c4333dcaac776b98f05465dfa083dbb31","tid":1708992,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ba206b92c6295ecbb495fd